{{Use mdy dates|date=April 2012}} {{Infobox Airline |airline = Tandem-Aero |logo = Tandem_Aero_Logo.jpg |logo_size = |fleet_size = |destinations = 1 |IATA = TQ |ICAO = TDM |callsign = TANDEM AERO |parent = |company_slogan = |founded = 1998 |headquarters = [[Chişinău]], Moldova |key_people = |hubs = [[Chişinău International Airport]] |secondary_hubs = |focus_cities = |frequent_flyer = |lounge = |alliance = |website = http://www.tandemaero.md/ }}
'''Tandem Aero''' is a passenger charter airline based in [[Chişinău]], Moldova. It was established in 1998 and transported 24,700 passengers in 2008.
==Operations== The airlines' air operators certificate permits the transport of passengers, goods and mail (at July 2007).<ref>{{cite web| title=Air Operators| date=July 5, 2007| work=Civil Aviation Authority of the Republic of Moldova| url=http://en.caa.md/air_operators| accessdate=July 6, 2007| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yepWlR8Q?url=http://en.caa.md/air_operators| archivedate=May 13, 2011| df=mdy-all}}</ref>
Tandem Aero operates a single international scheduled route to [[Tel Aviv]].
{|class="wikitable sortable toccolours" |- ! style="background:#318ce7; color:white;"|City ! style="background:#318ce7; color:white;"|Country ! style="background:#318ce7; color:white;"|IATA ! style="background:#318ce7; color:white;"|ICAO ! style="background:#318ce7; color:white;"|Airport ! style="background:#318ce7; color:white;" class="unsortable"|Refs |- |[[Chişinău]]||Moldova||align=center|KIV||align=center|LUKK|| style="background:#d0e7ff;"|[[Chisinau International Airport]] <sup>[Base]</sup>||align=center| |- |[[Tel Aviv]]||Israel||align=center|TLV||align=center|LLBG||[[Ben Gurion International Airport]]||align=center| |}
The flights to Kiev were operated with Antonov An-24 until March 2006. Due to air traffic disputes between Moldova and Ukraine the service was halted. After a long period without flights, Tandem Aero flew again to Kiev on 31.08.2006 with an Air Moldova Embraer 120. Later for some time Tandem Aero switched to its Antonov 24RV. As Moldova did not allow Aerosvit to fly on the route Chisinau-Kiev, Ukraine denied Tandem Aero the continuation of its service on this route starting February 6, 2007.
In February 2015, [[Air Moldova]] ended its leasing contract with Tandem Aero. Therefore, the [[Embraer EMB-120]] used for it has been phased out while the three operated routes to [[Sochi]], [[Bucharest]] and [[Kiev]] were terminated.<ref>http://ch-aviation.com/portal/news/36203-air-moldova-ends-embraer-120-operations</ref>
== Fleet == Tandem Aero operates aircraft leased from [[Air Moldova]], as of July 2016.<ref>http://www.airfleets.net/flottecie/Tandem%20Aero.htm</ref>
